title: Concerned GOP push Rand Paul to focus on Senate re-election
text: > Top News Concerned GOP push Rand Paul to focus on Senate re-election FILE - In this Oct. 9, 2015, file photo, Republican presidential candidate Sen. Rand Paul, R-Ky. speaks during a campaign stop at the Republican Liberty Caucus in Nashua, N.H. A defiant Paul is brushing off weak fundraising and weaker poll numbers as some Republicans begin pushing him to abandon his presidential ambitions to focus on his Senate re-election. The first-term Kentucky senator this week claimed his superior political organization would prove wrong those doubting his chances in the White House contest. (AP Photo/Jim Cole, File)
